{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e77a5c88-9e02-4efc-917f-c4520cbfece2","content":"**No, `net6.0` is not supported by MSTest v4.** MSTest 4.x dropped support for .NET 6.0 (which is already end-of-life). The minimum supported target frameworks are:\n\n- **.NET 8.0** (`net8.0`) or later\n- **.NET Framework 4.6.2** (`net462`) or later\n\nYou'll need to update your `TargetFramework` to at least `net8.0` before migrating to MSTest v4. Want me to make both changes (update the TFM and bump MSTest to v4)?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"447aef5a-be62-4624-9ba3-a0fa4423c35c","outputTokens":144,"requestId":"768C:25A610:47A93C:538650:69F2C231"},"id":"80ad6d34-5dc7-4c80-8811-88583536049f","timestamp":"2026-04-30T02:45:09.064Z","parentId":"71eb99cb-6e83-4e88-bb2b-df5258d98357"}
